{"tid":13124,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"d排骨死mk真係以為自己有2舊腹肌就好好抽","createTime":"2016-11-30T02:29:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T22:40:07.000Z","uid":22345,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e58737bbff5e70fae1d8a9c8bdbab44d0e7998","tid":13124,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:29:57.000Z","msg":"話說頭先我溝緊女<br />\n有條MK狗係咁話我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n(但其實我己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你癡左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小醜咁係到show佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"a8d2ed454c3fa8d835e0db2721d498674a078fd2","tid":13124,"uid":21964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:30:35.000Z","msg":"又回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da42eee12fc408507a36a6951ae92774ea64e3b","tid":13124,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nLihkg第一篇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8e66b80cbddcd80bfd5f0e8257772d4fbacf2ab","tid":13124,"uid":44724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:32:39.000Z","msg":"笑 想知道因咩事比人打到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7789b442b49447fa6f9436b709afc99a385a0dc4","tid":13124,"uid":22345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor